      units_en: "For each confidential cryptographic key documented in [E.Info.CCK-1.CCK] functionally assess whether\nthe CCK’s length as documented in [E.Info.CCK-1.CCK] is implemented in accordance with [E.Info.CCK-1.CCK.SecurityStrength].",
